Name       : ghostscript
Arch       : i386
Version    : 8.15.2
Release    : 9.11.el5
Size       : 18 M
Repo       : installed
Summary    : A PostScript(TM) interpreter and renderer.
URL        : http://www.cups.org/espgs/
License    : GPL
Description: Ghostscript is a set of software that provides a PostScript(TM)
           : interpreter, a set of C procedures (the Ghostscript library, which
           : implements the graphics capabilities in the PostScript language)
           : and an interpreter for Portable Document Format (PDF) files.
           : Ghostscript translates PostScript code into many common, bitmapped
           : formats, like those understood by your printer or screen.
           : Ghostscript is normally used to display PostScript files and to
           : print PostScript files to non-PostScript printers.
           : 
           : If you need to display PostScript files or print them to
           : non-PostScript printers, you should install ghostscript. If you
           : install ghostscript, you also need to install the ghostscript-fonts
           : package.

